body:
We'll have to modify VerifyLibsAndLicenses.java then, as  "compile-time" is only checked for GPL licenses (see [VerifyLibsAndLicenses.java:line 306](https://github.com/apache/incubator-netbeans/blob/9.0-alpha-rc2/nbbuild/antsrc/org/netbeans/nbbuild/extlibs/VerifyLibsAndLicenses.java))

Would you like me to add it to this PR or want a specific PR?
Also, is this pseudo-code correct?

```
    if (contains "GPL") {
        "Type: compile-time" is required.
        if (contains "GPL-2-CP") {
            "Comment" is required.
        }
    } 
    if ("Type: compile-time") {
        ignore rest of license checking
    }
```
